<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="mathml.xsl"?><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:pref="http://www.w3.org/2002/Math/preference" pref:renderer="mathplayer-dl"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /><title>glClientActiveTexture</title><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.69.1" /></head><body><div class="refentry" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="glClientActiveTexture"></a><div class="titlepage"></div><div class="refnamediv"><h2>Name</h2><p>glClientActiveTexture — select active texture unit</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><h2>C Specification</h2><div class="funcsynopsis"><p><code class="funcdef">void <b class="fsfunc">glClientActiveTexture</b>(</code>GLenum <var class="pdparam">texture</var><code>)</code>;</p></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4782010"></a><h2>Parameters</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>texture</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies which texture unit to make active. The number
                    of texture units is implementation dependent, but must be at least
                    two. <em class="parameter"><code>texture</code></em> must be one of 
                    <code class="constant">GL_TEXTURE</code><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">i</mml:mi></mml:math>,
                    where i ranges from 0 to the value of <code class="constant">GL_MAX_TEXTURE_COORDS</code> - 1, which is an
                    implementation-dependent value.  The initial value is
                    <code class="constant">GL_TEXTURE0</code>.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4781931"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">glClientActiveTexture</code> selects the vertex array client state parameters to be modified by
            <a href="glTexCoordPointer.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glTexCoordPointer</span></span></a>, and enabled or disabled with
            <a href="glEnableClientState.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glEnableClientState</span></span></a> or <a href="glDisableClientState.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glDisableClientState</span></span></a>, respectively,
            when called with a parameter of <code class="constant">GL_TEXTURE_COORD_ARRAY</code>.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768510"></a><h2>Notes</h2><p>
            <code class="function">glClientActiveTexture</code> is supported only if the GL version is 1.3 or greater, or
            <code class="code">ARB_multitexture</code> is included in the string returned by
            <a href="glGetString.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glGetString</span></span></a> when called with the argument <code class="constant">GL_EXTENSIONS</code>.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768540"></a><h2>Errors</h2><p>
            <code class="constant">GL_INVALID_ENUM</code> is generated if <em class="parameter"><code>texture</code></em> is not one of
            <code class="constant">GL_TEXTURE</code><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">i</mml:mi></mml:math>,
            where
            i ranges from 0 to the value of <code class="constant">GL_MAX_TEXTURE_COORDS</code> - 1.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768578"></a><h2>Associated Gets</h2><p>
            <a href="glGet.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glGet</span></span></a> with argument <code class="constant">GL_CLIENT_ACTIVE_TEXTURE</code> or <code class="constant">GL_MAX_TEXTURE_COORDS</code>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768600"></a><h2>See Also</h2><p>
            <a href="glActiveTexture.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glActiveTexture</span></span></a>,
            <a href="glDisableClientState.xml&#10;"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glDisableClientState</span></span></a>,
